rows.label: qst001402_msg0002
rows.name:
A capable Driver is truly
different, mo. That was
reasonably speedy, mo!

rows.label: qst001402_msg0003
rows.name:
Time is money, mo! Speed
is also money, mo!

rows.label: qst001402_msg0004
rows.name:
The value of one's life is determined
by how much one earns, mo.

rows.label: qst001402_msg0005
rows.name:
Well then, with that pearl of
wisdom, Pididi will speedily
transport the cargo to Alba Margen, mo.

rows.label: qst001402_msg0006
rows.name:
No more idle chatter,
mo! Thank you, mo!
